ng event with only hundreds of well-chosen pictures</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Heavy Ion Research","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='210'%3e%3cpath%20d='M75%2092v2h89v-5H75v3'%20fill='%2364ffda'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.9044368600682593,"src":"/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/91e18/heavy.png","srcSet":"/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/20862/heavy.png 175w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/98c8f/heavy.png 350w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/91e18/heavy.png 700w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/0a1b9/heavy.png 1050w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/1b32b/heavy.png 1116w","srcWebp":"/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/89afa/heavy.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/9fca7/heavy.webp 175w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/37a4e/heavy.webp 350w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/89afa/heavy.webp 700w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/78e7a/heavy.webp 1050w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/9efe5/heavy.webp 1116w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"tech":["ROOT","TMVA","C++"],"github":"","external":"https://zxqlxy.synology.me:5001/d/f/438834080071553799","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Analyzed the data of tens of millions of collisions of J/psi mesons and strange charm mesons collected from <a href=\"https://home.cern/science/accelerators/large-hadron-collider\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LHC</a>. Used boost decision tree, rectangular cut and MLP to train the data to get a better selection of the signal through <a href=\"http://tmva.sourceforge.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">TMVA</a>. Manipulated data stored in trees and visualized them via <a href=\"https://root.cern.ch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ROOT</a>. Optimized the C++ software in the Linux environment and increased the signal significance by 200%.</p>"}}]},"projects":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Deeplearning.ai","image":null,"tech":["TensorFlow","Jupyter Notebook","Python"],"github":"","external":"","show":"true"},"html":"<p>I implemented CNN to detect object (face and car) and style transfer with and without Tensorflow. I also implemented RNN (LSTM) to improvise Jazz and translate text</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Google MAP API Configure Maps","image":null,"tech":["JavaScript","Html","CSS"],"github":"","external":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/77326579","show":"true"},"html":"<p>I self-learned Google Map API to configure maps for Polaris &#x26; Dawn Consulting for clients. </p>"}}]},"extracurriculars":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"National Champion of International Physicsts Tournament","image":"","tech":[null],"github":"","external":"http://news.rice.edu/2019/12/16/undergraduate-team-wins-nationals-qualifies-for-world-cup-of-physics/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>• Was Part of the Rice team in IPT and competed with three other teams in Berkeley.</p>\n<p>• Won the first place after presenting and debating our proposal to the solutions to the problems.</p>\n<p>• Link to official site: <a href=\"https://2020.iptnet.info/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://2020.iptnet.info/</a>'</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Guid of International Young Physicsts Tournament","image":"","tech":[null],"github":"","external":"https://iypt.org/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>• Communicated with team Georgia to take care of their living and communication with the Tournament for 7 days</p>\n<p>• Provided technical and empirical help to teams in competition and helped the organizers to coordinate schedule and venue</p>"}}]},"contact":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Get In Touch"},"html":"<p>Although a physics and computer science major, I am also interested in photography, movies, art, traveling and fortune telling. In the processes of puesuing my interests, I get to know a lot more interesting people.</p>\n<p>So,  If you want to ask me anything or simply say Hi, I will respond!</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{}}}